### ğŸ›  å®Ÿè£… (Python)
```python
n = int(input())
numbers = list(map(int, input().split()))
numbers.sort(reverse=True)
alice_score = sum(numbers[0::2])
bob_score = sum(numbers[1::2])
ans = alice_score - bob_score
print(ans)
```
